Gut microbiota modulates neurotransmitter and gut-brain signaling
Shiyan Qu a,b,c,d,e,1, Zijin Yu a,b,c,d,e,1, Yaxuan Zhou a,b,c,d,e,1, Shiyi Wang a,b,c,d,e,
Minqi Jia a,b,c,d,e, Ti Chen f, Xiaojie Zhang a,b,c,d,e,*
